trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling av <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new entry in the container.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny oppføring i beholderen.

trans-unit.source: You must call the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A> method on the new entry to make the creation permanent.
trans-unit.target: Du må kalle den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>-metoden på den nye oppføringen foreta oppretting permanent.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: When you call this method, you can then set mandatory property values on the new entry.
trans-unit.target: Når du kaller denne metoden, kan du definere obligatorisk egenskapsverdier på den nye oppføringen.

trans-unit.source: The providers each have different requirements for properties that need to be set before a call to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A> method is made.
trans-unit.target: Leverandørene hver har ulike krav for egenskaper som må angis før et kall til den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>metoden utføres.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.CommitChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: If those requirements are not met, the provider might throw an exception.
trans-unit.target: Hvis disse kravene ikke er oppfylt, kan leverandøren Iverksett et unntak.

trans-unit.source: Check with your provider to determine which properties must be set before committing changes.
trans-unit.target: Kontakt leverandøren for å finne ut hvilke egenskaper må angis før å lagre endringene.

trans-unit.source: The name of the new entry.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den nye oppføringen.

trans-unit.source: The name of the schema that is used for the new entry.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på skjemaet som brukes for den nye oppføringen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> object that represents the new entry.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> objektet som representerer den nye oppføringen.

trans-unit.source: An error occurred during the call to the underlying interface.
trans-unit.target: Det oppstod en feil under kall til grensesnittet underliggende.

trans-unit.source: Returns the member of this collection with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer medlemmet i denne samlingen med det angitte navnet.

trans-unit.source: If child objects of different types have the same name, the first matching child object is returned.
trans-unit.target: Hvis underordnede objekter av forskjellige typer har samme navn, returneres det første underordnede-objektet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The Internet Information Services (IIS) provider does not support this method.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For Internet Information Services (IIS) leverandøren støtter ikke denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: Use the overloaded <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntries.Find%2A> method and specify an empty string ("") for the `schemaClassName` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av overbelastet <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntries.Find%2A>metoden og angi en tom streng ("") for den `schemaClassName` parameteren.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntries.Find%2A>

trans-unit.source: > > If no matching result is found, a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException> with error code 0x2030 is thrown.
trans-unit.target: >> Hvis det finnes ingen samsvarende resultat, en <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException>kode 0x2030 er registrert med feil.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException>

trans-unit.source: Contains the name of the child object for which to search.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder navnet på det underordnede objektet det skal søkes etter.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> that represents the child object that was found.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> som representerer det underordnede objektet som ble funnet.

trans-unit.source: The Active Directory Domain Services object is not a container.
trans-unit.target: Active Directory Domain Services-objektet er ikke en beholder.

trans-unit.source: An error occurred during the call to the underlying interface.
trans-unit.target: Det oppstod en feil under kall til grensesnittet underliggende.

trans-unit.source: Returns the member of this collection with the specified name and of the specified type.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer medlemmet for denne samlingen med det angitte navnet og for den angitte typen.

trans-unit.source: If no matching result is found, a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException> with error code 0x2030 is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes ingen samsvarende resultat, en <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException>kode 0x2030 er registrert med feil.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesCOMException>

trans-unit.source: The name of the child directory object for which to search.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på mappen det underordnede objektet det skal søkes etter.

trans-unit.source: The class name of the child directory object for which to search.
trans-unit.target: Klassenavnet for mappen det underordnede objektet det skal søkes etter.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> object that represents the child object that was found.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> objektet som representerer det underordnede objektet som ble funnet.

trans-unit.source: The Active Directory Domain Services object is not a container.
trans-unit.target: Active Directory Domain Services-objektet er ikke en beholder.

trans-unit.source: An error occurred during the call to the underlying interface.
trans-unit.target: Det oppstod en feil under kall til grensesnittet underliggende.

trans-unit.source: Returns an enumerator that iterates through the collection.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en opplisting som går gjennom samlingen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>objekt som kan brukes til å gå gjennom samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Deletes a member of this collection.
trans-unit.target: Sletter et medlem i denne samlingen.

trans-unit.source: If the entry to be removed is a container, the container must be empty.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det skal fjernes er en beholder, må beholderen være tom.

trans-unit.source: To delete a container and all its children, use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.DeleteTree%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil slette en beholder og alle underordnede verdier, kan du bruke den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.DeleteTree%2A>metoden.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.DeleteTree%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"></xref> object to delete.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry"> </xref> objektet som skal slettes.

trans-unit.source: An error occurred during the call to the underlying interface.
trans-unit.target: Det oppstod en feil under kall til grensesnittet underliggende.

trans-unit.source: Gets the schemas that specify which child objects are contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter skjemaene som angir hvilken underordnede objektene, i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: If the SchemaFilter property is empty, child objects of all types are visible in the collection; otherwise, only those of the specified types are visible.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen SchemaFilter er tom, er underordnede objekter for alle typer synlige i samlingen. Hvis ikke vises bare de angitte typene.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.SchemaNameCollection"></xref> that specifies which child objects are contained in the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntries"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.SchemaNameCollection"> </xref> som angir hvilken underordnede objektene, i den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntries"> </xref> forekomsten.
